{"tid":2375784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★支水乾了！港股收跌479點　北水淨流入大減","createTime":"2021-01-22T09:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T05:33:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3f0ff8b01f4b5867d6a432c42b8f8ee498a177","tid":2375784,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"港股突破三萬點後，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>北水流入明顯減慢</strong></span>，大市隨即回吐。恒生指數周五(22日)低開118點後跌幅擴大，最多挫514點，低見29,413點；收市報29,447點，跌479點或1.6%，全周升873點。國企指數收報11,677點，跌212點或1.78%；科技指數跌44點或0.45%，收報9,765點。主板全日成交2,441億港元，港股通淨買入縮至93.67億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210122/bkn-20210122092049072-0122_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210122%2Fbkn-20210122092049072-0122_00842_001.html&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=ac871a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210122/bkn-20210122092049072-0122_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3664c64644d4801e5c37a1d1d5361fec5bab5b88","tid":2375784,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"need more 9 vegtable<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35419249cecfc359bd2c9e9c269ce3a549addbc4","tid":2375784,"uid":103262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"Still 流入<br />\nWill rise next week<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac1e5085b4e1ece730471ba1f1031026a8abf7c","tid":2375784,"uid":103262,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3664c64644d4801e5c37a1d1d5361fec5bab5b88","tid":